author: davidlt
body:
We are moving to Protocol Buffers 2.6.1 from 2.4.1. New version does not
have any issues compiling with GCC 6.0.0 (r233941). In addition to that
2.4.1 is a 5 year old release. Remember that Protocol Buffers provide
forward and backward compatibility for written data.

How files were regenerated?

```
cd $CMSSW_BASE/src
protoc --cpp_out=. DQMServices/Core/src/ROOTFilePB.proto
```

Signed-off-by: David Abdurachmanov David.Abdurachmanov@cern.ch
title: Regenerate DQMServices/Core/src/ROOTFilePB.proto
